ectrum%20below).%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ch3%3EItems%20of%20note%3C%2Fh3%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20The%20basic%20audio%20element%20of%20this%20demo%20is%20a%20pair%20of%20simple%20waves%20of%0A%20%20different%20frequencies%2C%20which%20are%20played%20in%20unison.%20You%20can%20pick%0A%20%20among%20a%20few%20options%20for%20the%20basic%20waveform%3A%0A%0A%20%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cli%3Esine%20%E2%80%94%20Sine%20waves%20are%2C%20harmonically%2C%20the%20simplest%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20possible%20waveforms.%20They%20generally%20have%20a%20%22pure%22%20sound%20to%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20human%20ears%2C%20which%20might%20remind%20you%20of%20a%20kalimba%20(finger%20piano).%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cli%3Etriangle%20%E2%80%94%20Triangle%20waves%20are%20simple%20geometrically%2C%20yet%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20harmonically%20rich%20and%20mellow%20to%20human%20ears.%20The%20sound%20might%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20remind%20you%20of%20a%20marimba%20(wooden%20xylophone).%20This%20is%20the%20default%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20waveform%20choice%2C%20as%20this%20is%20the%20choice%20made%20by%20Keen%20in%20his%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20original%20composition.%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cli%3Esawtooth%20%E2%80%94%20Sawtooth%20waves%20tend%20to%20sound%20buzzy%20and%20a%20bit%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20harsh%20to%20human%20ears.%20The%20sound%20might%20remind%20you%20of%20a%20reed%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20instrument%20such%20as%20an%20oboe%20or%20clarinet.%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Cli%3Esquare%20%E2%80%94%20Square%20waves%20also%20have%20a%20buzziness%20about%20them.%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20The%20sound%20might%20remind%20you%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20recorder%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20(woodwind).%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Fli%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20The%20notes%20played%20by%20this%20demo%20are%20picked%20randomly%20from%20two%20octaves%20in%20an%0A%20%20equal-tempered%20pentatonic%20scale.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20scale%20that%20is%20often%0A%20%20encountered%20in%20Western%20music%2C%20however%20it%20happens%20to%20make%20for%20note%0A%20%20pairs%20and%20transitions%20that%20are%20pleasing%20to%20human%20ears.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20The%20waveform%20is%20intentionally%20level-quantized%20to%20simulate%20low%20bit-depth.%0A%20%20You%20can%20see%20this%20quantization%20in%20the%20oscilloscope%20as%20%22stair%20steps%22%20which%0A%20%20are%20most%20visible%20in%20gently-sloping%20portions%20of%20the%20waveform.%20(That%20is%2C%0A%20%20the%20stair%20steps%20are%20%3Ci%3Enot%3C%2Fi%3E%20a%20visual%20artifact%20from%20the%20oscilloscope%0A%20%20rendering%2C%20but%20rather%20an%20accurate%20reflection%20of%20the%20waveform%0A%20%20being%20generated.)%20In%20terms%20of%20the%20sound%20you%20hear%2C%20this%20quantization%0A%20%20causes%20a%20quiet%20high-pitched%20%22shimmering%22%20effect.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%0A%20%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdanfuzz%2Fmimu%2Ftree%2Fmain%2Fawkward-js-music%22%3E%0A%20%20See%20the%20source%3C%2Fa%3E.%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Ctable%20class%3D%22footer%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20Copyright%202015-2025%20the%20Mimu%20Authors%20(Dan%20Bornstein%20et%20alia).%3Cbr%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20SPDX-License-Identifier%3A%20Apache-2.0%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3Ctd%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fmilk.com%2F%22%3Emilk.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22..%2F%22%3Emimu%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%20%20%20%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%20%20%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%0A%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
